I normally don't write reviews, but this game deserves one, found it randomly on steam weekend deal and oh boy.. i'm glad i did

Game is amazing, the best hide n seek game i ever played; 
Devs are really active and constantly updating the game;
There's 2 gamemodes and a bunch of maps that you can enjoy for hours;

I would recommend playing with friends, but the community of this game is really amazing and i already found some people to play together and have fun
No need to wait for sale, game is a great deal at full price

